Package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.builders

Class IDPManager

java.lang.Object
com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.builders.IDPManager
public class IDPManager extends Object
IDPManager provides a loose abstraction over processing insulin delivery profile (IDP) response manages, generating the requests necessary to get a full state of the profiles on the pump, and generating request messages in the correct format for making mutations on pump profiles.
